Period = enum
  pOverall = "overall", p7day = "7day", p1month = "1month", p3month = "3month",
  p6month = "6month", p12month = "12month"
Used by userTopAlbums, userTopArtists, and userTopTracks to represent the "period" field.   Source   Edit 
TaggingType = enum
  ttArtist = "artist", ttAlbum = "album", ttTrack = "track"
Used by userPersonalTags to specify what type of tags should be returned by the API method call.   Source   Edit
